    "values": [
      "AakZad Crypt Priest: The Architect of Bone-Frequency",
      "Medium",
      "Construct/Biomechanical",
      "",
      "While the AakZad soldiers are engines of war, the Crypt Priest is the cold, calculating intelligence that keeps their mechanical hearts beating. Draped in tattered, oil-stained vestments smelling of ozone and ancient dust, the Priest’s body is a terrifying fusion of skeletal remains, humming brass gears, and glowing filaments. It does not breathe; it vibrates. By manipulating the \"Spirit-Echo\"—the resonant frequency of the void—it tunes reality itself to shatter stone or knit metal to bone. When it speaks, it bypasses the ears, vibrating a grinding stone melody directly into the listener's marrow.",
