    "values": [
      "Aakzad Knotted Giant",
      "Giant",
      "Construct/Biomechanical)",
      "",
      "A towering monument of bone and metal, the Knotted Titan is a patchwork of necrotized muscle held together by glowing green filaments of energy that act as external tendons. Where the Crypt Priest is the transmitter of the bone-frequency, the Titan is its most violent output. Its massive cleavers are fused directly into its arm-stumps, vibrating so intensely with necrotic energy that they leave a trail of sickly green light in the air as they swing. It possesses no mind of its own, driven entirely by the grinding frequency of its masters to shatter the enemy's frontline.",
