    "values": [
      "Aakzad Warrior: The Resonant Legionnaire",
      "Medium",
      "Construct / Biomechanical",
      "",
      "A single Aakzad Warrior is a marvel of \"calcified geometry.\" Their armor plates aren't strapped on; they are extruded directly from the marrow, forming a seamless, humming shell of white-grey bone interlaced with dark, oily conduits. They do not breathe, but their chests rhythmically expand and contract to vent the searing heat of their internal engines. They carry Vibration-Blades that don't just cut meat, but shatter molecular bonds. In groups, their collective humming becomes a physical weight in the air—a drone that matches the heartbeat of their enemies, forcibly syncing it to their own cold, mechanical rhythm.",
