    "values": [
      "AakZad: Biomechanical Harvester",
      "Large",
      "Construct/Biomechanical)",
      "",
      "A terrifying fusion of two souls into one biomechanical engine of war. The AakZad appears as a centauroid nightmare; the \"rider\" is fused at the waist into a ribcage of reinforced alien alloy, while the \"beast\" possesses far too many joints. They share a singular consciousness, linked by a glowing necrotic-green or violet pulse that acts as their nervous system. They do not charge like living horses—they scuttle up walls, pivot 180 degrees in a fraction of a second, and move with a disturbing, multi-limbed fluidity that completely ignores the traditional physics of momentum.",
