    "values": [
      "Abomination",
      "Giant",
      "Undead / Monstrosity",
      "",
      "The Abomination is a towering, nauseating monument to forbidden sorcery. It is not born, but \"knotted\" together from a chaotic mass of necrotized muscle and jagged bone shards harvested from a dozen different corpses. It hums with a sickly green necromantic tether—a visible, pulsing vein of emerald light that serves as a secondary nervous system, allowing it to instantly re-knit severed limbs and seal gaping wounds in seconds. It does not think, feel, or tire. It wields its massive, rusted cleavers with the unstoppable, rhythmic momentum of a slaughterhouse machine, turning the battlefield into a literal charnel house.",
