    "values": [
      "Air Elemental Lord: The Sky-Tearer",
      "Enormous",
      "Elemental Lord",
      "",
      "The Lord of Air does not appear as a simple cloud, but as a towering, translucent titan of storm and pressure. Its body is composed of \"Hard Air\"—atmosphere so compressed it shines like diamond—swirled with living lightning and the dark violet of a brewing supercell. It does not speak in words; its voice is the sound of a mountain-side shattering under a hurricane, a resonance that can collapse lungs. To stand before the Sky-Tearer is to realize the ground is merely a suggestion. It commands the \"High Winds,\" a celestial frequency that can strip the skin from bone or lift entire fortresses into the stratosphere.",
