      "Air Elemental: The Living Zephyr",
      "Large",
      "Elemental",
      "",
      "A swirling vortex of translucent vapor, dust, and crackling static. While it can take a vaguely humanoid shape with broad shoulders of thunderclouds and eyes of sheet lightning, it is never truly solid. It is constant motion, roaring like a canyon wind. They are the most temperamental of the elementals—they don't walk, they flow; they don't strike, they buffet. Summoned by high-altitude sorcerers, they view grounded creatures with a detached pity, fighting not with blades, but by weaponizing the atmosphere itself.",
