      "Archangel",
      "Giant",
      "Celestial / Divine",
      "",
      "An Archangel stands roughly 14 feet tall, appearing as a flawless humanoid figure composed of luminous platinum. They do not wear physical armor; their very presence acts as an impenetrable barrier. They possess four wings resembling stained glass, refracting the sun into blinding geometric patterns. They carry no physical weapons, often keeping their hands folded in prayer or raised in absolute authority. Their power comes from their throat—a vibrating resonance of \"Holy Frequency.\" They do not cast spells; they issue Decrees that the universe is forced to obey. When they speak, the ground trembles, and mortal souls instinctively drop to their knees.",
