      "Ash-Blight Dragon: The Extinction Event",
      "Enormous",
      "Dragon / Primordial",
      "",
      "The Ash-Blight Dragon is not merely a predator; it is a localized extinction event. Older than recorded history, these colossal wyrms make their lairs in shattered volcanoes and dead lands—environments they actively create. The dragon's internal heat is so intense that the very air around it turns to superheated white ash. It does not negotiate or hoard gold; it hoards absolute dominion. Its colossal frame is armored in jagged scales resembling cooled obsidian, glowing with a molten orange heartbeat from within. To face an Ash-Blight Dragon is to fight the raw, unchained fury of the earth.",
