      "Basilisk: The Stone-Gazer",
      "Large",
      "Fantasy Lizard",
      "",
      "\"The first thing you'll notice is the silence. No birds, no insects—just a garden of statues, frozen in expressions of absolute terror. If you feel a hot, chemical breath on your ankles, it's already too late.\" The Basilisk is a low-slung, heavy-bodied reptilian predator with eight powerful legs that allow it to scale cavern walls with terrifying speed. Its mottled, toxic green scales shimmer with a poisonous, oily sheen, and a jagged crimson crest crowns its head. Its most lethal feature is its pale, glowing yellow eyes, which project a primordial magical force capable of turning blood to silt and flesh to flint in a matter of seconds.",
