    "values": [
      "Beastman Shaman: The Horned Oracle",
      "Medium",
      "Humanoid / Beastman",
      "",
      "While a typical Beastman relies on a rusted axe and raw sinew, the Shaman finds power in the rot of the woods and the alignment of blood-moons. Draped in molted furs, clattering bone charms, and smelling of wet dog and ozone, they serve as the spiritual anchors of the warband. They don't \"study\" magic; they seize it like a predator catching prey. Their rituals are loud, messy, and involve the rhythmic beating of hooves against the earth to churn up the \"Old Winds\"—the raw, unfiltered essence of nature's spite.\n\nCasting Details - The Old Winds",
