      "Beastman Warrior: The Horned Grunt",
      "Medium",
      "Humanoid / Beastman",
      "",
      "A nightmare of muscle, coarse fur, and jagged iron. Standing a head taller than most men and significantly wider, they are built for the \"crush.\" They don't fight with the discipline of a soldier or the grace of a duelist; they fight with the desperate, explosive energy of a cornered predator that has finally broken free. In battle, they are a wall of noise—bleating, roaring, and the rhythmic clatter of hooves on stone. They despise civilization, taking perverse joy in hacking down stone monuments and burning silk",
