    "values": [
      "Bin Uluhm Engineer Overseer: The Iron Tyrant",
      "Medium",
      "Humanoid / Artificer",
      "",
      "The Engineer Overseers are the dark architects of Bin Uluhm. Encased in bulky, steam-hissing volcanic exoskeletons, they rarely walk when they can ride a mechanized walker or simply lumber forward on pneumatic leg-braces. They possess a terrifying intellect dedicated entirely to the art of mass destruction and subjugation. They do not fight with mere swords; they wield explosive alchemy, pneumatic hammers, and clockwork horrors. To them, the lives of their slaves and soldiers are merely resources to be spent testing a new weapon.",
