    "values": [
      "Blue Dragon: The Storm of the Dunes",
      "Enormous",
      "Dragon",
      "",
      "A Blue Dragon is a magnificent and terrifying sight. Its scales are the deep, iridescent blue of a desert sky at midnight, polished to a mirror-sheen by the abrasive sands. A singular, massive horn projects from its snout—a lightning rod for the static energy that constantly hums through its body. They are patient hunters, burying themselves beneath the sand for days until a caravan passes overhead, erupting in a shower of glass and electricity. They possess an immense ego and a particular obsession with gems (especially sapphires), often sparing a \"lesser being\" if offered a worthy tribute.",
      "5",
