    "values": [
      "Bog Octopuss (Silt Lurker)",
      "Giant",
      "Beast / Monstrosity",
      "",
      "A master of camouflage, its skin mimics the texture of wet moss, decaying logs, and oily peat. It doesn't swim so much as it \"drifts\" through the mud, using eight muscular tentacles to pull itself along the swamp floor or hang from low cypress branches. Unlike its oceanic cousins, it secretes a thick, paralytic mucus to \"marinate\" prey. It is the silent killer of the marsh—one moment you’re stepping on a log, the next, you’re being dragged into the dark, anaerobic depths. It prefers to strike from total concealment, waiting for the heaviest member of the party to walk over it before erupting in a whirlwind of suction cups and slime.",
