    "values": [
      "Bone Giant: The Amalgamation",
      "Giant",
      "Undead / Construct",
      "",
      "The ultimate weapon of a master necromancer. It is not a resurrected creature, but an amalgamation—a golem of death constructed from the fused skeletons of hundreds of humans, horses, and beasts. The bones are lashed together by thick, glowing sinews of sickly-green necromantic energy, and inside its hollow ribcage, a localized storm of trapped souls swirls like a vortex. It wears no armor; its outer layer of fused skulls and femurs acts as a hardened carapace. It moves with a jerky, unnatural rhythm, but its sheer stride length makes it terrifyingly fast. Wielding an uprooted graveyard mausoleum pillar on chains, it exists only to smash castle gates and crush armored formations into dust.",
      "5",
