    "values": [
      "Chaos Dwarf: The Lava-Forged (Bin Uluhm Taskmaster)",
      "Medium",
      "Humanoid / Corrupted",
      "",
      "Hailing from the molten, volcanic depths of Bin Uluhm, these corrupted kin of the Dwarves have traded their honor for dark industry and infernal pacts. Their beards are singed and woven with jagged obsidian shards, their skin stained with soot and ash. Instead of building for the sake of the craft, they build engines of war and chains for the enslaved. Fueled by spite, burning malice, and the oppressive heat of their lava-forged home, they wield serrated blades and crude, explosive black-powder weapons, acting as ruthless, unforgiving taskmasters.",
