    "values": [
      "Chaos Dwarf: The Slag-Drudge",
      "Medium",
      "Humanoid / Corrupted",
      "",
      "The lowest of the low in the Bin Uluhm hierarchy. While the Taskmasters wield cruel whips and the Overseers build mighty machines, the Slag-Drudges are the miserable, soot-covered laborers who shovel the magma and haul the volatile black-powder. They are barely treated better than the slaves, clad in literal scrap iron and cooled slag strapped to their burned skin. They are half-blind from the forge-glare, deafened by industry, and fight out of sheer, terrified desperation and malicious spite.",
