    "values": [
      "Cherubim: The Iron-Beast",
      "Giant",
      "Celestial / Construct",
      "",
      "A Cherubim is a massive, four-legged entity standing 18 feet tall, its body forged from a living alloy of celestial bronze and iron. It possesses four distinct wings covered in thousands of flickering, golden eyes that see into every spectrum of existence—infrared, magical, and moral. Its most unsettling feature is its head, which continuously rotates to reveal four distinct faces: the Man (Wisdom), the Lion (Might), the Ox (Endurance), and the Eagle (Agility). Depending on which face is currently forward, the Cherubim’s fighting style shifts instantly. They are the ultimate \"Living Weapon,\" designed to guard the gates of reality from anything that would dare approach the High Seat.",
