      "Chimera: The Living Chaos",
      "Large",
      "Monstrosity",
      "",
      "The Chimera is a staggering blasphemy of nature—a fusion of Lion, Goat, and Dragon. It is the ultimate \"Chaos-Factor\" in combat, as each head operates with its own intent, allowing the creature to breathe fire, gore with horns, and rend with claws all in the same breath. A nightmare stitched together from the scrap heap of creation, it is what happens when Nature has a mid-life crisis. Commonly found in rocky crags or desolate ruins, the Chimera is more than just a multi-headed beast—it is a three-way civil war held together by a single, bloodthirsty nervous system.",
