  {
    "values": [
      "Chromatic Dragon: The Sovereign (The Five-Fold Ruin)",
      "Titanic",
      "Dragon / Mythic",
      "",
      "The Sovereign is a terrifying sight. Her main body is covered in scales that shift and shimmer like oil on water, showing glimpses of every chromatic color. She possesses five long, serpentine necks, each ending in a head representing a different element. To face her is to face five different bosses at once. Each head has its own personality and its own \"initiative\" in combat. She doesn't just attack; she creates a symphony of elemental destruction where fire melts what the ice has frozen, and acid dissolves what the lightning has shattered.",
