      "Cloud Giant: The Masked Noble",
      "Enormous",
      "Giant / Elemental",
      "",
      "Standing 30 feet tall, these gilded aristocrats of the sky wear masks of frozen mist and flowing silks that defy gravity. They do not merely live in the sky; they weaponize the very atmosphere, crushing intruders under the sheer weight of the air itself. High-ranking nobles wear masks of \"cloud-silver\" that change expression based on their current mood, from aloof amusement to terrifying wrath. Adorned in jewelry carved from sky-sapphires and silks that never stain, their very presence feels expensive, intimidating, and suffocating to lesser beings.",
