    "values": [
      "Crypt Guard: The Eternal Sentry",
      "Medium",
      "Undead / Construct",
      "",
      "A harrowing sight—a skeleton draped in the rusted, pitted remains of once-glorious plate armor. Frayed tabards bearing faded heraldry hang from their ribcages. They simply stand in the dark, their hollow eye sockets glowing with cold blue balefire. Unlike common undead, the Crypt Guard retains the muscle memory of its former life. They move with a chilling, mechanical precision, interlocking shields as if still on the battlefields of the living. To them, every living thing is a grave robber, and the only penalty for trespassing is a cold blade to the heart.",
