    "values": [
      "Daemon Lord: The Abyssal Strategist",
      "Large",
      "Fiend / Daemonic",
      "",
      "Standing between 8 and 10 feet tall, the Daemon Lord possesses an aura of dark majesty that is almost physical, forcing even the most chaotic spirits to bow. Forged from the soul-stuff of fallen heroes, his armor is immaculate, and he carries a blade that can sever a soul with a scratch. When he speaks, reality itself tries to obey. He does not merely lead through strength, but through a supreme, cold intellect that views the mortal realms as a chessboard. To him, a Greater Daemon is simply an expensive, violent siege engine to be deployed and discarded.",
