    "values": [
      "Daemon Prince: The Ascended Favored",
      "Medium",
      "Fiend / Aberration (Former Mortal)aemon",
      "",
      "The ultimate \"teacher's pet\" of the Chaos Gods. Because they were once mortal, they possess a cruel, personal ambition that pure-blood daemons lack. They are walking trophies, adorned with \"gifts\" like crystalline skin, wings of shifting smoke, or armor fused directly to their nervous system. They are arguably more dangerous than older daemons because they understand humanity perfectly—they know how to break a knight's oath or exploit a wizard's pride. Other daemons respect them out of envy; they know the Prince is the \"Favored Son,\" and to strike him is to invite the direct wrath of the gods.",
