      "Dark Elf: Noktorian Gutter-Blade",
      "Medium",
      "Humanoid",
      "",
      "The bottom feeders of the Obsidian Chasm. While the Night-Blades are elite assassins, the Gutter-Blades are the desperate street-rats, scavengers, and disposable pawns of Noktorian society. Wrapped in soot-stained rags and wielding chipped, rusted shivs, they lurk in the darkest crevices of the subterranean city. They are underfed, uneducated, and entirely devoid of loyalty. They fight like cornered vermin—striking only when they have overwhelming numbers, using dirty tricks, and fleeing at the first sign of genuine danger.",
