      "Medium",
      "Humanoid",
      "",
      "Hailing from Noktoria, the Obsidian Chasm, these dark kin are the ruthless, subterranean mirrors of the Thalasien Elite. Where their surface cousins glide with stoic grace, the Night-Blades slink through absolute darkness clad in shadow-silk that seems to absorb light. They are sadistic, thriving on psychological warfare, cruel taunts, and lethal poisons. They do not fight fair; they strike from the ceiling, poison the air, and vanish before a counterattack can be mounted. To fight a Noktorian is to fight your own paranoia in the dark.",
