      "Displacer Beast: The Phase-Stalker",
      "Medium",
      "Monstrosity / Beast",
      "",
      "A predatory masterpiece of illusion. A sleek, six-legged feline with obsidian fur, it is constantly surrounded by a shimmering haze. This isn't magic it casts, but a biological property of its hide that bends light, making the beast appear to be several feet away from its actual position. It stalks its prey from the shadows, using its unnatural geometry and twin spiked tentacles to tear apart its victims before they even know where to swing their swords.",
