    "values": [
      "Dog - War: The Loyal Anchor",
      "Medium",
      "Beast",
      "",
      "A true War Dog is a mountain of corded muscle and scarred leather. Usually of a mastiff or wolfhound lineage, these beasts are outfitted with spiked collars and light leather or chain barding. They don't bark at shadows; they wait for the command to tear the throat out of whatever is lurking within them. In a world of magic and monsters, the War Dog serves as a grounded anchor. Their nose can smell a Shaman’s ozone or a Daemon's rot long before a human eye sees a flicker in the treeline. They aren't just pets; they are tactical partners that prioritize their master's life above their own.",
