    "values": [
      "Dwarf: Kel Thurum Militiaman (\"Iron Joe\")",
      "Medium",
      "Humanoid",
      "",
      "Not every Dwarf is a runed-plate elite. \"Iron Joe\" is the backbone of Kel Thurum: the miner, the mason, the brewer, and the smith. Drafted into the local militia when danger threatens the lower gates, they march to war in thick leather aprons, iron caps, and whatever heavy tool they were just using. They lack the flawless tactical discipline of the Royal Guard, but they make up for it with sheer, blue-collar stubbornness, callous-thick skin, and a complete refusal to back down from a fight—especially if they've already had a pint.",
