    "values": [
      "Dwarf: The Living Stone (Kel Thurum Defender)",
      "Medium",
      "Hmanoid",
      "",
      "A masterpiece of compact power. Standing a head shorter than a man but weighing just as much, they are built of broad shoulders and thick, weathered skin. Their beards are braided with gold and iron, telling the tale of their lineage. To a Dwarf, the world is a series of things to be built, mined, or defended. Hailing from the capital city of Kel Thurum, they possess a \"hard mind\"—a stubbornness bordering on the supernatural. They are the ultimate survivors, thriving in the dark, airless depths.\n\nThese are the elite guard hailing from Kel Thurum, the Dwarven Capital City.",
