    "values": [
      "Earth Elemental (Greater)The Mountain-Heart",
      "Giant",
      "Elemental / Construct",
      "",
      "A Greater Earth Elemental is not merely formed from rock; it is bedrock given catastrophic motion. These titans are composed of entire ranges of obsidian, iron, and granite, forged over millennia by intense geothermal pressures. Its face is a blocky mask of smooth stone with deep eye sockets glowing with the orange light of a geothermal core. Where a standard Elemental is merely heavy, the Greater variant is gravity itself. They are fused with large, pulsating emerald geodes—their \"Mountain-Heart\"—that anchor their sentience and generate a localized gravitational field. In its wake, forests are pushed aside, the ground is pulverized, and loose rocks fall upward.",
