      "Earth Elemental (Lesser) The Ruble Clod",
      "Medium",
      "Elemental",
      "",
      "A chaotic, barely held-together amalgamation of loose dirt, jagged rocks, and torn roots. It lacks the deliberate humanoid shape of its larger kin, appearing more like a rolling, shambling mound of animated debris. It is completely mindless and moves with a sluggish, dragging gait, leaving a trail of mud and gravel in its wake. It doesn't strategize or understand formations; it simply lumbers forward and clumsily tries to bury whatever is in front of it.",
