    "values": [
      "Earth Elemental Lord: The World-Root",
      "Enormous",
      "Elemental Lord",
      "",
      "The Lord of Earth is a gargantuan entity that resembles a mountain range forged into a sentient, humanoid shape. Its body is composed of ultra-dense \"Singularity Granite\" and pulsating obsidian, held together by a core of molten gold and raw crystalline power. Its head is a jagged peak of indestructible quartz with eyes like twin suns burning within the deep crust. Where the Air Lord is erratic and swift, the Earth Lord is inevitable. It is the master of Gravitational Law. To stand in its presence is to feel your own bones creak under doubled gravity. It is the absolute authority on stability—it can turn a raging sea to solid salt or a fortress to liquid sand with a single thought.",
