      "",
      "A massive, bi-pedal construct composed of ancient granite and deep-vein ore. Unlike lesser forms, the Vanguard has a rough, deliberate humanoid shape. Its \"face\" is a blocky mask of smooth stone with two eyes glowing with the intense, orange light of a geothermal core. It moves with a terrifying, crushing rhythm—a slow but unstoppable stride that pulverizes the ground beneath its feet. It doesn't just block enemies; it seeks to turn them into pulp.",
