      "None",
      "Passive Traits\nAura of Serenity: Any creature starting its turn within 60ft must pass a Willpower (9) test or lose all hostile intent for 1 turn.\n\nRooted Wisdom: Verdantus is a permanent part of the forest and is immune to being pushed, tripped, or moved against his will.\n\nPhotosynthetic Regrowth: As long as it is daylight or magic light is present, Verdantus regains 10 Wounds at the start of every turn.\n\nAction-Based Abilities\nWhispers of the Weald (1 Action): Shares a fragment of ancient lore. The target ally gains a +1 bonus to their next three rolls.\n\nEntangling Roots (TN 8 - 2 Actions): Verdantus commands the earth to rise. Target is Grappled (Def 0) and must pass a Physique test to break free.\n\nSeismic Slam (3 Actions): Verdantus strikes the ground. All enemies within 20ft must pass an Agility test or fall Prone and take 3d10 Wounds."
