      "Elf: Thalasien Conscript",
      "Medium",
      "Humanoid",
      "",
      "Not every resident of the silver-leafed city is an ancient, stoic blademaster. The conscripts are the artisans, poets, and youths—Elves who have barely seen their fiftieth autumn—drafted into the militia when dire threats approach. They possess the natural, weightless grace and sharp eyes of their fey bloodline, but they are fragile and entirely unaccustomed to the brutal realities of war. Armed with simple hunting bows and ceremonial daggers, they fight with desperate, trembling speed rather than cold precision.",
