      "Elf: Thalasien Elite Guard",
      "Medium",
      "Humanoid",
      "",
      "Hailing from the pristine, silver-leafed city of Thalasien, these elite guards are the pinnacle of martial grace. Clad in lightweight, gilded armor that moves like silk, they wield curved glaives and longbows with terrifying, cold precision. They don't block; they deflect. They don't march; they glide. They are stoic and utterly silent on duty, communicating through subtle hand signs. To face a Thalasien Elite Guard is to fight the wind itself—sharp, sudden, and seemingly untouchable.",
