      "Essence Scryer",
      "Medium",
      "Monster",
      "",
      "The Scryer is not made of flesh. It is a series of interlocking, moving crystalline plates that form a shifting sphere about the size of a human torso.\n\nThe Material: The crystal isn't clear; it is an oily, iridescent black, like polished obsidian that refracts light in an unnatural way (chromatic aberration).\n\nThe \"Eye\": In the very center of the sphere, where the plates don't quite meet, is a perfect vacuum. Suspended within that void is a core of swirling, cyan-white energy. This is not a biological pupil; it is a stabilized arcane singularity. It doesn't look at you; it stares through you.\n\nThe Scryer is Hovering. It ignores difficult terrain (rubble, water, pits) and can maintain an altitude of up to 30 ft.",
