      "Fimir Witch Queen: The Meargh",
      "Large",
      "Humanoid / Spellcaster",
      "",
      "Standing nearly 8 feet tall when fully upright, the Witch Queen is a haunting figure of bog-born majesty. Unlike the bald warriors of her clan, she is unique for the long, lank hair that hangs from her scalp like rotting willow strands. Her skin is a pale, sickly olive, stretched over a barrel-chested frame that possesses immense hidden strength. Her most striking feature is a single, oversized milk-white eye that glows with an inner, baleful light. She rarely carries a traditional weapon, instead clutching a gnarled staff of petrified bog-wood adorned with human fingerbones and \"power of 3\" resonance stones. Surrounded by a clinging, sentient mist that moves at her command, she appears more like a ghost than a physical creature.",
