      "",
      "The younger, less magically developed kin of the Fen-Ghuls. They are still massive, hunchbacked brutes with saurian tails, but they lack the deep, primal connection to The Mists. Unable to conjure thick fog banks themselves, they instead lurk in naturally occurring swamp miasma or follow in the wake of a Fen-Ghul's conjured storms. Armed with crude driftwood clubs and their own heavy tails, they are simple-minded, aggressive shock-troops. Their jaundiced skin constantly weeps a slippery, toxic bile, making them incredibly difficult to pin down in a melee brawl.",
