    "values": [
      "Fire Elemental Lord: Sol-Invictus",
      "Enormous",
      "Elemental Lord",
      "",
      "A gargantuan entity composed of \"White-Hot Singularity Plasma\" and swirling, dark magma pressurized into solid armor. Its core is a hyper-concentrated diamond-blue geode, pulsing with celestial-level heat. Its face is a blocky mask of smooth, dark stone with intense eyes glowing with fierce blue light. It moves with a terrifying, rhythmic thud—a slow but unstoppable stride that melts the ground into vitrified glass. Voluminous, blazing flame-whips of orange, red, and blue fire lash from its massive hands, while dense plumes of black and gray smoke erupt from its fissures. Its presence is a walking supernova that consumes the very atmosphere. Sol-Invictus does not just attack; it initiates a Total Thermal Event to vaporize all opposition and unmake local geography.",
