    "values": [
      "Fire Elemental: The Ember-Sprite",
      "Medium",
      "Elemental",
      "",
      "A flickering, waist-high manifestation of living heat. It doesn't have a solid form, appearing instead as a dancing core of white-hot plasma surrounded by a shifting body of orange and red flames. It moves with a frantic, crackling energy, leaving scorched footprints and a trail of black soot wherever it glides. Unlike other elementals, the Ember-Sprite is hyper-aggressive; it views everything organic as fuel. It emits a constant sound like a roaring hearth, and the air around it shimmers with a heat haze that makes its exact movements difficult to track.",
