    "values": [
      "Fire Elemental: The Solar Core",
      "Large",
      "Elemental",
      "",
      "A primeval force of nature, often manifesting near active volcanoes or summoned to incinerate fortresses. Standing around 15 feet tall, it is a towering humanoid shape composed of roiling white and orange flames. Its \"skin\" is a shifting shell of semi-solid magma that constantly cracks to reveal a blinding, spinning solar core within. It does not walk; it flows like a lava current, melting the ground into glass with every step. To stand near it makes your skin blister and your breath catch as the air itself becomes a searing liquid.",
