    "values": [
      "Fire Giant: The Forge-Father",
      "Giant",
      "Giant / Elemental",
      "",
      "A massive humanoid standing 18 to 20 feet tall, with skin the color of cooled basalt and hair that glows like smoldering embers. Their bodies are built like heavy-duty anvils—broad, dense, and seemingly immovable. They are almost never seen without their \"Singe-Plate\" armor, massive slabs of black iron bolted directly into their flesh or held by thick, heat-resistant chains. They live in the hearts of volcanoes, crafting weapons for gods and titans. In battle, they move with a heavy, rhythmic deliberation. They don't rush; they advance like a wall of lava, wielding weapons so hot they can slice through stone walls as if they were warm wax.",
