      "Frost Giant: The Ice-Raider",
      "Giant",
      "Giant / Elemental",
      "",
      "Towering at 22 feet, the Frost Giant is a hulking monolith of glacial ice and corded, pale muscle. Draped in the heavy pelts of slain megafauna and wearing armor crafted from unmelting, diamond-hard permafrost, they emerge from the blizzards like walking avalanches. Their eyes are solid, pupilless orbs of pale blue, and their breath spills from their lungs as a thick, freezing fog. They view the world as a battlefield where only the \"Hardened\" survive. A blizzard is not a storm to be feared, but a cloak to be worn. Masters of the \"Glacial Siege,\" they use their incredible strength to trigger avalanches or hurl boulders coated in permafrost that shatter like shrapnel upon impact.",
