      "Gelatinous Cube: The Dungeon Janitor",
      "Large",
      "Ooze / Aberration",
      "",
      "A 10-foot cube of shimmering, translucent protoplasm. These are mindless organisms that drift silently through dungeon corridors, \"cleaning\" the floors of organic matter, bones, and discarded gear. Nearly invisible in low light, the only way to spot one is often to notice the floating \"leftovers\" of its previous meals—swords, coins, and skulls—suspended mid-air within its body. It does not hunt; it simply sweeps, absorbing anything foolish enough to stand in its path.",
