  {
    "values": [
      "Ghost: The Restless Spirit",
      "Medium",
      "Undead / Incorporeal",
      "",
      "A translucent, glowing apparition bound to the mortal plane by unfinished business, sudden trauma, or a terrible curse. They appear as shifting, faded echoes of who they were in life, often bearing the gruesome phantom wounds of their demise. They do not walk; they drift silently, bringing an unnatural, bone-deep chill wherever they roam. A Ghost doesn't care about your heavy plate armor or your physical strength—it bypasses the flesh entirely to strike directly at the soul.",
      "7",
