    "values": [
      "Giant Ape: The Silverback Titan",
      "Giant",
      "Beast / Primordial",
      "",
      "Deep within the uncharted, primordial jungles rules the Silverback Titan. Standing over twenty feet tall when fully upright, this ancient apex predator is fiercely territorial and highly intelligent. Its body is corded with impossibly dense muscle and covered in coarse, iron-grey hair thick enough to turn away arrows. It does not hunt for sport; it hunts to eliminate threats to its domain. The Titan fights with brutal, sweeping strikes that shatter trees and crush armor, using the jungle itself as a weapon by ripping up boulders and trunks to hurl at distant interlopers.",
      "6",
      "4",
