      "",
      "A carriage-sized nightmare of chittering mandibles and bristling, barbed hairs. The Giant Spider dwells in lightless caverns and ancient, overgrown forests, spinning webs strong enough to ensnare a galloping horse. Its eight multifaceted eyes gleam with a cold, predatory intelligence, and venom constantly drips from its jagged, iron-hard fangs. It brings the creeping, visceral horror of the unseen ambush to the battlefield, turning the environment itself into a lethal, sticky snare.",
