      "Gnoll: The Scavenger of the Wastes",
      "Medium",
      "Humanoid (Beastkin)",
      "",
      "A bipedal nightmare with the unsettling features of a hyena, the Wasteland Gnoll stands roughly the height of an average human. They are wiry, heavily muscled scavengers clad in patchwork armor stitched from rusted steel and cured hides. Operating in ruthless, giggling packs, they do not fight for honor or territory; they fight because the scent of blood demands it. They are brutal frontline raiders, notorious for running down exhausted prey and leaving nothing but splintered bone in their wake.",
