      "Goblin Shaman: The Cave-Whisperer",
      "Small",
      "Humanoid / Spellcaster",
      "",
      "The Cave Goblin Shaman is the dark, pulsating heart of the subterranean swarm. While standard goblins are driven by hunger and malice, the Shaman is guided by the whispers of ancient, restless cave spirits. Physically weak and frail, they rely entirely on their terrifying mental fortitude and deep connection to the metaphysical realm to dominate their tribe. Draped in bone charms that act as magical focal points, the air around them permanently smells of copper and ozone. When threatened, they vanish into a cloud of toxic green mist, reappearing across the cavern only to summon blood-drenched totems that drive their lesser kin into a frenzied, unkillable state.",
