    "values": [
      "Goblin: The Night-Cutter",
      "Small",
      "Humanoid / Goblinoid",
      "",
      "A Night-Cutter stands roughly 3 to 4 feet tall, with a wiry, lean body and skin the color of bruised plums or stagnant moss. Their oversized ears constantly twitch, catching the slightest sound of approaching footsteps, and their wide, needle-toothed mouths are usually twisted into a mocking grin. They are never found alone; where there is one, ten more lurk in the shadows. Clad in \"Scrap-Plate\" made from hammered pot lids and rusted chain, they wield jagged, filth-coated blades and \"Boom-Pots\" filled with unstable alchemical sludge. They value winning over honor, and will scatter the moment a fight turns against them—only to return minutes later with reinforcements.",
