      "Titanic",
      "Dragon / Celestial",
      "",
      "A majestic, serpentine titan covered in scales of actual organic metal, harder than any forged steel. Their heads are feline and regal, featuring long, flowing whiskers that crackle with static energy and a mane of metallic hair. They act as the \"Final Arbiters\" of the world. Famous for walking among mortals, they often spend centuries as humble scholars or advisors before revealing their gargantuan, radiant nature to enforce cosmic balance. If a war threatens to unbalance reality, an Aureate Sovereign descends to impose a magical treaty—or incinerate both sides.",
