    "values": [
      "Grand Arcanist of the Third Order",
      "Medium",
      "Humanoid / Spellcaster (Hero)",
      "",
      "A legendary spell-weaver who has synchronized their mind across three different planes of magic. Clad in the intricate, floating vestments of the Third Order, their eyes hum with raw, contained cosmic energy. They carry no blades or armor, viewing physical combat as a crude relic of lesser minds. A Grand Arcanist does not merely cast spells; they unravel and rewrite the physics of the battlefield. When they unleash their power, the air screams, and their spells hit with the apocalyptic kinetic force of a siege engine without them ever lifting a physical weapon.",
      "2",
