      "Grave Wolf: The Earthen Sentinel",
      "Medium",
      "Undead / Beast",
      "",
      "The Grave Wolf is the reanimated remnant of a hunting hound or wild wolf, twisted by dark magic to serve as an eternal sentinel for crypts and burying grounds. They are gaunt and horrifying; patches of matted, rotting fur cling to exposed ribs and jagged bone, and pale, green balefire burns in their empty eye sockets. They do not hunt for meat, but for the warmth of the living. They are known to burrow silently through the loose soil of graveyards, erupting from the earth to drag interlopers down into the dark.\n\nMove 30 Ground / 20 Burrow",
