      "Greater Daemon: The Herald of Ruin",
      "Enormous",
      "Fiend / Daemonic",
      "",
      "Standing over 30 feet tall, the Herald of Ruin is a towering nightmare of jagged obsidian horns, rippling crimson muscle, and tattered, leathery wings that blot out the sun. It wields an Abyssal Greatblade forged from the agonizing souls of the damned, and hellfire constantly bleeds from its eyes and maw. It does not merely destroy cities; it corrupts the very geometry of the world around it. The sky boils into a bruised, toxic purple in its presence, and the earth turns to scorched glass beneath its hooves. To face the Herald is to stare directly into the abyss and watch it smile back.",
