      "Large",
      "Beast / Monstrosity",
      "",
      "The Griffon is the undisputed king of the mountain peaks, a terrifying but majestic fusion of a golden eagle and a tawny lion. Possessing a massive wingspan and razor-sharp talons capable of piercing plate armor, they are brutal ambush predators that strike from the sun. They are fiercely territorial and proudly untamable, viewing anyone who enters their alpine hunting grounds as either a threat to their nest or their next meal. They do not fight fair; they rely on blinding dives, snatching their prey into the sky before the victim's allies can even draw their swords.\n",
