      "Half-Ogre: The Pit-Bred Bruiser",
      "Large",
      "Humanoid (Giant-Kin)",
      "",
      "A brutal crossbreed combining human cunning with the raw, terrifying mass of an ogre. Often raised in underground fighting pits or outlaw mercenary camps, they stand 8 to 9 feet tall, characterized by thick, sloping brows, jutting underbites, and heavily scarred, leathery skin. They are significantly smarter than full-blooded ogres but possess enough of their giant-kin heritage to effortlessly rip a man's arm from its socket. In the grim underworlds and mercenary companies, a Half-Ogre is a terrifying asset. They serve as enforcers, shock troops, and warlord bodyguards, clad in scavenged, mismatched iron plate and wielding weapons far too heavy for a normal human to lift.",
