      "Halfling: The Slip-Step",
      "Small",
      "Humanoid",
      "",
      "The Halfling: The Slip-Step\nStanding roughly three feet tall, Halflings are diminutive, quick-footed folk often underestimated by the larger races of the world. What they lack in raw physical might, they make up for with astonishing agility, sharp senses, and an uncanny, almost supernatural well of luck. They tend to wear practical, earth-toned clothing and padded leather, moving with a silent grace that makes them exceptional scouts, thieves, or ambushers.\n\n",
