      "Harpy: Siren of the Canyons",
      "Medium",
      "Monstrosity (Avian)",
      "",
      "From a distance, their voices weave a tragic, hypnotic lullaby that echoes through the canyons, compelling travelers to step just a little closer to the cliff's edge. Up close, the illusion shatters. A Harpy is a vile, stench-ridden fusion of a feral humanoid and a scavenging bird of prey. They have hollow bones, filthy, razor-sharp talons, and eyes completely devoid of empathy. They do not fight fair; they lure, they swoop, they bleed their prey, and they let gravity do the rest of the work.",
