      "Havenspire City Watchman",
      "Medium",
      "Humanoid (Human)",
      "",
      "The First Line\nWhile the Elite Guard protect the capital's VIPs and fortresses, the City Watchmen walk the muddy streets, patrol the outer walls, and keep the peace in the bustling markets. They are lightly armored in chain shirts and padded leather, wearing the crisp white and gold tabards of Havenspire. Armed with standard-issue spears and wooden shields, they rely on numbers, basic training, and a sharp eye. A single Watchman is rarely a lethal threat to a seasoned adventurer, but they are never truly alone. Their greatest weapon is the brass signal whistle around their neck.",
