      "Humanoid (Human)",
      "",
      "The capital city of Havenspire does not entrust its safety to mere mercenaries or peasant militias. The Elite Guard are the finest soldiers the realm has to offer, hand-picked for their physical prowess and unwavering loyalty. Clad in gleaming, interlocking plate armor forged in the capital's grand foundries, they are striking figures of authority. They fight with a cold, calculated precision, utilizing heavy tower shields and masterwork longswords. They are not mindless monsters or savage raiders; they are professional sentinels whose sole purpose is to hold the line, protect the city's VIPs, and pacify threats with methodical, overwhelming defense.",
