      "Hobgoblin Phalanx Leader",
      "Medium",
      "Humanoid (Goblinoid)",
      "",
      "For a Goblinoid - The Iron Elite\nHobgoblins are the martial elite of their kind. They stand roughly as tall as a human but possess a much broader, denser muscular frame. Their skin ranges from a dark, leathery orange to a deep iron-red. They are rarely seen without their equipment; a Hobgoblin’s social standing is dictated by the quality of their kit and the discipline of their unit. The Phalanx Leader wears a well-oiled coat of banded mail and carries a long-reaching halberd, allowing them to coordinate their troops from behind a line of shields while still delivering devastating strikes.",
