    "values": [
      "Hydra: The Ever-Hungry",
      "Giant",
      "Monstrosity (Reptilian)",
      "",
      "A Hydra is a mountain of reptilian muscle, covered in slick, swamp-stained scales that range from deep charcoal to sickly bile-green. Its most terrifying feature is, of course, its multiple heads—each mounted on a long, serpentine neck that can move with the speed of a striking cobra. Each head possesses its own rudimentary intelligence, allowing the beast to track, snap at, and swallow multiple foes simultaneously. They radiate a thick, musk-like stench of rot and stagnant water. To fight a Hydra is to enter a race against time; the creature is famously difficult to kill because its blood is supercharged with regenerative mutagens. If a head is severed, the stump cauterizes and splits almost instantly, sprouting two more aggressive, hungrier versions of the original.",
