      "Ice Troll: The Glacial Behemoth",
      "Large",
      "Monstrosity (Troll)",
      "",
      "Indigenous to the highest, most unforgiving glacial peaks, the Ice Troll is a terrifying adaptation of the troll lineage. Standing 10 feet tall, its pale blue skin is thick and leathery, pierced by jagged shards of true-ice that grow directly out of its bones. It does not bleed liquid blood; it bleeds a sub-zero slush that flash-freezes upon hitting the air. When an Ice Troll is wounded, it doesn't just knit its flesh back together—it pulls the ambient moisture from the air to pack its wounds with solid ice, making it harder to kill the longer a battle lasts.",
