    "values": [
      "Iron-Minotaur: The Blood-Gorgon",
      "Medium",
      "Monstrosity (Mutant / Brute)",
      "",
      "A horrifying mutation of giant-kin and dark alchemy, the Iron-Minotaur is built for pure, unstoppable slaughter. Standing over ten feet tall, its flesh is fused with dark iron, and its very skeletal structure is composed of metallic bone that regularly protrudes through its heavily scarred skin. Most terrifyingly, it possesses four massive, heavily muscled arms, each gripping a crude, rusted cleaver or battleaxe. Driven entirely by a supernatural blood-greed, the Gorgon does not tire and does not retreat. It wades into the thickest phalanxes, its four arms working like a mechanical meat-grinder, turning disciplined formations into a spray of red mist.",
      "4",
