      "Kobold: The Warren Menace",
      "Small",
      "Humanoid (Reptilian)",
      "",
      "Standing no taller than a human child, the Kobold is a scaly, reptilian humanoid with a snout resembling a small dragon and eyes that gleam with nervous, malicious energy. What they lack in physical strength and bravery, they more than make up for in sheer numbers, ruthless cunning, and an almost unnatural talent for engineering traps. They are rarely found alone, preferring the dark, cramped tunnels of their warrens where they can ambush intruders from the shadows before scattering into the crevices. Entering a Kobold den is incredibly dangerous, as every corridor is filled with tripwires, pit traps, and falling rocks.",
