      "Kraken: The Abyssal Titan",
      "Titanic",
      "Monstrosity (Aquatic/Titan)",
      "",
      "A nightmare of the deep, the Kraken is a monstrosity of writhing tentacles, crushing beaks, and eyes the size of galleons. Existing as a Titanic class entity, its sheer mass warps the battlefield. Its hide is thick enough to snap harpoons, and its immense strength can drag entire warships into the abyss. It does not simply fight its enemies; it acts as a natural disaster, overwhelming them with impossible reach and devastating, sweeping blows. To face the Kraken is to fight the ocean itself.",
