      "Krox: Swamp Behemoth",
      "Giant",
      "Monstrosity (Reptilian)",
      "",
      "Towering at over sixteen feet tall and thick with overlapping slabs of dense, reptilian muscle, the Krox is a true Giant utilized by the Lizardmen to break enemy lines and shatter fortifications. They are not particularly intelligent, often needing to be heavily chained and directed by smaller Skinks or Chieftains between battles. Once unleashed, however, they become a mindless, walking natural disaster of thrashing tails, snapping jaws, and devastating sweeps from crude, massive weapons. To stand before a charging Krox is to invite being crushed into the mud, a fate many armored knights have suffered when underestimating the sheer kinetic force of the swamp's heaviest hitters.",
