      "Lesser Daemon: The Warp-Skitterer",
      "Medium",
      "Fiend / Daemonic",
      "",
      "Lesser Daemons are the jagged glass of the chaotic realms. They rarely have a stable physical form, often appearing as a nauseating mix of spindly limbs, too many eyes, and mouths that open in places they shouldn't. They don't walk so much as they \"glitch\" through reality, moving in terrifying, jerky bursts of speed. They are driven by an overwhelming hunger to drag the order of the mortal world back into the screaming maw of the void. Weak alone, in a \"muttering swarm\" they can overwhelm seasoned veterans through sheer sensory overload.",
