      "Lizardman Chieftain: The Apex",
      "Large",
      "Humanoid (Reptilian / Hero)",
      "",
      "Deep in the suffocating heat of the ancient swamps, the Apex Chieftain rules by overwhelming biological supremacy. Standing over nine feet tall—a massive, hulking mutation compared to their kin—their scales are thick, scarred, and faded to a dull, iron-like grey. They wear the skulls of rival predators as trophies and wield massive weapons carved from bone and jagged obsidian. An Apex Chieftain fights with the terrifying, explosive economy of motion belonging to a giant crocodile. They are cold, calculating, and capable of tearing an armored knight in half or shattering a shield wall with a single swing.",
