      "Magma-Caller (The Vein-Witch)",
      "Medium",
      "Pyreborn / Caster",
      "",
      "\"A sight of terrible beauty, often older than the Vanguards. Her skin is almost entirely translucent in places, revealing the brilliant, flowing copper-gold of her 'Sun-Blood' beneath. Wearing robes of woven asbestos-fiber and obsidian plates, she carries a Core-Staff tipped with a smoking 'Primordial Spark.' In battle, she is slow and stationary, acting as a literal 'Hearth' for her people, reshaping the battlefield by raising walls of cooling slag and opening fissures that spew toxic gases. To a Magma-Caller, the enemy is not a person, but an 'impurity' in the landscape that must be smelted away.\"\n\n(Often guarded by Thralls or Warriors)",
