      "Malakor, The Monarch of Midnight",
      "Enormous",
      "Shadow / Cosmic Entity",
      "",
      "Malakor is a gargantuan, terrifyingly elegant figure standing nearly 25 feet tall. His body is a shifting column of absolute darkness, possessing six slender, elongated arms ending in obsidian needles. He wears the \"Crown of Cold Starlight\"—shards of a dead sun that pulse with a rhythmic, pale light. He does not speak; he broadcasts his thoughts directly into the minds of those nearby, a sensation described as \"frozen liquid pouring into the ears.\" He views the material world as a flickering candle that must be snuffed out.",
