      "Manticore",
      "Giant",
      "Wild Beast",
      "",
      "A blasphemous fusion of beasts, the Manticore possesses the muscular body of a massive dire lion, the leathery wings of a dragon, and a grotesque, almost human-like face boasting three rows of razor-sharp teeth. Protruding from its hindquarters is a segmented, chitinous scorpion tail dripping with caustic black venom. As a Large (Lg) creature, it uses its immense physical power and flight to isolate and destroy prey, savoring the terror it inflicts just as much as the flesh it consumes.",
