      "Medusa: The Gorgon Queen",
      "Medium",
      "Monstrosity (Cursed Humanoid)",
      "",
      "Once a figure of enchanting beauty, the Medusa is a creature warped by ancient, spiteful magic. Her lower half is the thick, muscular tail of a massive viper, propelling her silently across the stone floors of her ruined lairs. Where hair once flowed, a writhing nest of venomous serpents hisses and strikes at any who draw near. She is a master of isolation, using her terrifying gaze to freeze her prey in place before filling them with arrows and venom. To fight her is to fight your own instincts, as looking upon her face spells eternal doom.",
