      "Midnight-Hound (Shadow Stalker)",
      "Large",
      "Shadow / Beast",
      "",
      "The Gloom-Tracker\nA terrifying distortion of a canine form. Standing nearly 4 feet at the shoulder, their bodies are elongated and hairless, covered in skin like wet, black leather. Lacking eyes entirely, their skull is a sleek, armored plate of bone. They hunt via sensitive, vibrating pits that detect the \"heat\" of a soul and the vibration of a heartbeat. They don't growl; instead, they emit a synchronized, low-frequency hum felt deep in the marrow, hunting with liquid precision to bleed their prey dry.",
