      "Minotaur: The Labyrinthine Terror",
      "Large",
      "Monstrosity",
      "",
      "A towering monstrosity standing over ten feet tall, the Minotaur possesses the heavily muscled body of a giant and the ferocious head of a primordial bull. As a Large creature, the Minotaur moves with a terrifying, thundering momentum that belies its sheer bulk. They are rarely found in the open, preferring to stalk the shadowed corridors of ancient ruins, catacombs, and cursed labyrinths where their prey has no room to escape. A Minotaur does not just kill; it demolishes, using massive weapons and its own thick-skulled horns to batter victims into unrecognizable pulp.",
