      "Moss-Revenant",
      "Medium",
      "Undead",
      "",
      "A tragic and horrifying fusion of death and parasitic nature, the Moss Revenant is the animated corpse of a fallen warrior, completely overtaken by a sentient, necrotic swamp flora. Existing as a Medium (Med) creature, it moves with a slow, deliberate, and unnerving stiffness. Beneath its rusted, waterlogged armor, its muscles and veins have been entirely replaced by thick, pulsing vines and dense green moss. It feels no pain, possesses no fear, and relentlessy pursues the living to use their corpses as fertilizer for the dark swamp.",
