    "values": [
      "Mummy: The Cursed Sovereign",
      "Medium",
      "Undead",
      "",
      "Awakened from a millennial slumber, the Mummy is a terrifying testament to ancient burial rites and forbidden necromancy. Existing as a Medium creature, it is entirely wrapped in hardened, resin-soaked linens and adorned with tarnished, cursed gold. It does not sprint or charge; instead, it marches with a slow, terrifying inevitability. The true horror of the Mummy lies not just in its supernatural physical strength, but in the potent, rotting curses that radiate from its desiccated form. To breathe the air around it is to feel your lungs fill with tomb dust and your lifeforce begin to wither.",
