      "Nightmare Butcher (Shadow Stalker)",
      "Large",
      "Shadow / Monstrosity",
      "",
      "The Sightless Carver\nDeep in the most gore-stained corners of the wild or the lightless damp of urban slaughterhouses dwells the Nightmare Butcher. A grotesque masterpiece of anatomical horror, it is a towering, four-armed mass of slab-like muscle. Its face is a smooth, sloping expanse of pale, scarred flesh with no eyes. Its primary arms grip rusted cleavers with bone-crushing strength, while secondary tentacle-like appendages snake out from its ribs to pin prey. Despite its bulk, it moves in nauseating, fluid silence, sliding through shadows like spilled oil.",
