    "values": [
      "Nightmare Spider: The Umbral Steed",
      "Large",
      "Shadow / Beast (Mount)",
      "",
      "A masterpiece of dark biology and sinister engineering. Its exoskeleton is polished to a mirror-like obsidian finish, heavily fitted with \"Light-Eater Armor\"—delicate plates of void-forged metal that hum with a low psychic frequency. Its padded feet are perfectly silent, allowing this massive beast to trot across marble floors or cavern ceilings without a single sound. It perceives the Ethereal Plane, tracking prey through solid walls, and spins razor-thin, psychic silk that cuts like cold piano wire rather than trapping like normal webbing.",
