    "values": [
      "Ogre",
      "Large",
      "Hmanoid",
      "",
      "A mountain of grotesque fat, matted hair, and slab-like muscle, the Ogre is driven by a single, overriding instinct: an insatiable, endless hunger. Standing nearly ten feet tall, it easily falls into the Large (Lg) size category. While they lack the tactical cunning of a Minotaur or the martial discipline of a Lizardman Chieftain, Ogres are walking siege engines of pure, blunt force. They do not wear forged armor, relying instead on rolls of thick, leathery blubber that easily swallow the blades of standard swords.",
