    "values": [
      "Ogre Witch-Doctor: The Blood-Speaker",
      "Large",
      "Humanoid (Giant-Kin / Caster)",
      "",
      "The Witch-Doctor is a horrifying anomaly among ogres: one that has discovered the power of the spirit realm by consuming the brains of human wizards and elven seers. Adorned in rattling bone fetishes, bleached skulls, and crude totems of dried blood, they channel the chaotic, hungry magic of the \"Great Maw.\" They do not cast elegant, academic spells. Instead, they vomit curses, boil the blood of their enemies, and hurl unstable elemental magic through rhythmic stomping and guttural, throat-tearing chants. To face a Blood-Speaker is to face a wizard trapped inside the body of a siege engine.",
