    "values": [
      "Orc Chieftain: The Iron-Breaker",
      "Large",
      "Orc / WarBoss",
      "",
      "To become a Chieftain in the Orcish war-host, one must not only be the strongest, but the most violently relentless. The Iron-Breaker is a towering mountain of green muscle and jagged, bolted scrap-iron armor. He wields a massive, two-handed executioner's axe that looks more like a slab of sharpened anvil than a traditional weapon. Whether charging on foot or surveying the carnage from the back of his Wyvern, he bellows orders that inspire terrifying bloodlust in his warriors. He doesn't just want to defeat his enemies; he wants to break their lines, their armor, and their spirit in a single, deafening charge.",
