    "values": [
      "Orc: Green Tide Grunt",
      "Medium",
      "Humanoid (Orc)",
      "",
      "Before an Orc earns their scars and bulks up into a frontline terror, they start as Grunts. Smaller, leaner, and constantly bullied by their larger kin, Grunts form the rushing, chaotic vanguard of the Green Tide. They are clad in the rusted, discarded scraps of previous campaigns and wield crudely sharpened choppers. Individually, a Grunt is a sloppy, reckless combatant who relies on wild swings rather than martial discipline. However, they are rarely encountered alone; they swarm the battlefield in shouting, spit-flying mobs, eager to kill a hero and claim the gear needed to elevate their rank in the warband.",
