    "values": [
      "Orc: The Green Tide Vanguard",
      "Large",
      "Humanoid (Orc)",
      "",
      "The backbone of the \"Green Tide,\" the Orc is a hulking, broad-shouldered humanoid with moss-colored skin, protruding tusks, and a temperament built for eternal warfare. Classified as a Medium creature, they lack the massive size multipliers of Ogres, but they make up for it with sheer aggressive tenacity. An Orc does not retreat; they view every scar as a badge of honor and every broken blade as a challenge to kill with their bare hands. They are the perfect middle-ground combatant—sturdier than a human and far more violent.",
