      "Owlbear: The Silent Ravager",
      "Large",
      "Monstrosity",
      "",
      "A furious, lumbering mass of feathers, fur, and muscle. It hunts with eerie silence in the dark, closing the distance before unleashing a flurry of armor-rending claws and a bone-crushing beak. A terrifying, heavily muscled apex predator, the Owlbear combines the crushing physical strength of a bear with the silent ferocity and acute senses of a giant owl. Because it is Large, its physical capabilities are significantly multiplied, allowing it to snap the spines of forest intruders as easily as dry kindling.",
