      "A majestic, winged equine radiating celestial energy. Highly prized as a mount for pure-hearted champions, the Pegasus uses its Large size not for sheer brutality, but for unmatched aerial mobility and divine defensive capabilities. Born from sea foam and star-fire, the Pegasus is a creature of absolute grace. In combat, it is a blur of white feathers and flashing hooves, capable of breaking enemy lines from above before carrying its rider to safety.",
