      "Giant",
      "Fiend (Devil / Boss)",
      "",
      "The ultimate general of the infernal armies. A towering, winged monstrosity of hardened scales and roaring hellfire. As a Giant-sized creature with incredibly high Intellect, Willpower, and Physique, it dominates both physical combat and dark magic seamlessly. Wrapped in a cloak of literal hellfire and wielding a massive mace forged from the souls of the damned, the Pit Fiend is a master of dark strategy and brutal subjugation. It does not just kill; it conquers. To face a Pit Fiend is to stand against the organized, inevitable march of Hell itself.",
