      "Medium",
      "Humanoid (Pyreborn)",
      "",
      "The Pyreborn are the ultimate survivalists of the extreme. Culturally, they are the world’s greatest smiths and pyromancers, viewing fire not as a destroyer, but as the \"Loom\" of reality. Encased in heat-treated bronze and obsidian that would cook a normal human alive, they advance with the steady, unstoppable momentum of a lava flow. A Sun-Forged warrior does not dodge or retreat; they simply march forward, trusting their master-crafted armor to shatter enemy blades while they reduce the opposition to ash and slag.",
