      "Rat Ogre: The Alchemical Abomination",
      "Large",
      "Vermin",
      "",
      "A grotesque, alchemically mutated horror of the deep sewers, the Rat Ogre is a towering, hunched monstrosity of hyper-developed muscle, patchy diseased fur, and rusted scrap metal violently bolted directly into its flesh. Standing at eight feet tall but fighting with a feral, scrambling gait, it possesses the raw, overwhelming Large (Lg) mass of an Ogre combined with the twitchy, predatory speed of a starving rat. Driven completely mad by its own unnatural growth, it thrashes wildly through subterranean tunnels, destroying anything in its path.",
