      "1-3",
      "Rusted Scrap Grafts, Alchemical Tubes/Injectors.",
      "Scavenged Metal Blades / Feral Claws",
      "Throwing Object/Rock",
      "Passive Traits\nDiseased Grafts: Any creature that takes Melee damage from the Rat Ogre must pass a Physique(6) test or gain the Infected condition, taking 5 unmitigable Wounds at the start of their next turn due to the filth and rust.\n\nFeral Senses: Its hyper-developed snout and twitching whiskers allow it to navigate and hunt in total darkness. It ignores all To-Hit and Defense penalties associated with fighting in low light or absolute pitch-black environments.\n\nFilth-Born: Having been born and mutated in the absolute worst alchemical runoff and raw sewage, the Rat Ogre is completely immune to all Disease and Poison conditions.\n\nWarp-Spasm: When the Rat Ogre is reduced to less than half of its Total Wounds, its alchemically altered blood boils. It immediately gains +1 Action per turn, but suffers a -2 penalty to its Defense as it abandons all self-preservation to tear its enemies apart.\n\nAction-Based Abilities\nRusted Warp-Cleaver (Melee - Cost: 2 Actions): Wielding a massive, jagged slab of rusted iron bolted to a sewer pipe, the Rat Ogre delivers a frenzied, sweeping chop. This 2-Handed heavy strike is fueled by its massive Physique and multiplied by its Large size, dealing a devastating 1d10 + 60 wounds. On an unmodified 9 or 10, the rusted metal inflicts 1 Bleeding condition.\n\nRabid Snapping Bite (Melee - Cost: 1 Action): Lunging forward with its elongated, foam-flecked snout, the beast clamps down with yellowed incisors. This 1-Handed natural attack deals 1d10 + 30 wounds. The victim must pass a Physique(7) test or immediately suffer 1 Disease condition from the horrific bacteria coating its teeth.\n\nSewer Grate Toss (Range - Cost: 1 Action): Ripping an iron grate or chunk of masonry from the tunnel walls, it hurls the heavy debris with terrifying speed. Combining its Agility and its Physique, multiplied by its size, this thrown projectile deals 1d10 + +30 blunt wounds on impact."
