      "Ratman Brood-Guard",
      "Medium",
      "Humanoid (Beastkin)",
      "",
      "The elite soldier caste of the ratmen burrows. While the Scavengers rely on sheer numbers and surprise, the Vanguards are disciplined, well-fed, and heavily armored. Standing taller and broader than their scavenging kin, the Vanguards are the true military force of the ratmen. Clad in scavenged, rust-pitted chainmail and wielding heavy, jagged halberds, they hold the line in the claustrophobic depths. They are ruthless, organized, and fiercely loyal to their brood-mothers, forming deadly phalanxes in the narrow tunnels of the underworld that break the momentum of invading forces.",
