      "Ratman Scavenger: The Filth-Born",
      "Medium",
      "Humanoid (Beastkin)",
      "",
      "Twisted, bipedal rodents that infest the deep sewers and forgotten caverns beneath civilized cities. Operating in the shadows, they rely on quick strikes, overwhelming numbers, and the virulent diseases they carry to wear down stronger opponents. Hunched and twitchy, the Ratman is a survivor of the deepest filth. Clad in stitched-together scrap leather and wielding rusted, filth-encrusted blades, they are cowards when alone but viciously bold when attacking in a pack. They do not fight with honor; they fight to survive.",
