      "Red Dragon: The World-Ender",
      "Titanic",
      "Dragon",
      "",
      "A titan of muscle and crimson scales thick as castle walls. Its breath is a mixture of sulfur and liquid flame, and a constant heat shimmer surrounds its body, making the air ripple like a desert mirage. Its horns are a crown of jagged obsidian, and its eyes glow with the white-hot intensity of a forge. Red Dragons are famously arrogant, viewing all of creation as their rightful hoard and \"lesser races\" as temporary stewards of their gold. When a Red Dragon takes flight, the sky turns the color of blood, and the temperature for miles around begins to climb.",
