    "values": [
      "Riding Horse: Traveler's Companion",
      "Large",
      "Beast",
      "",
      "The unsung hero of the civilized world, the Riding Horse is the backbone of travel, trade, and communication. Unlike their heavier, armor-clad Warhorse cousins, riding horses are bred for endurance, speed, and a smooth gait. They are highly intelligent for beasts and fiercely loyal to a gentle rider, but their instincts remain tied to survival. When the scent of a troll hits the wind or a fireball shatters the night, a Riding Horse’s primary directive is to run. They are not combatants; they are the reliable, swift engines that ensure adventurers live to see the next town.",
