    "values": [
      "Seraphim: The Six-Winged Arbiter",
      "Giant",
      "Celestial (Boss)",
      "",
      "The Seraphim are the burning ones, the highest echelon of the celestial host. Descending from the heavens on six wings of pure, blinding light, they are the wrath of the divine made manifest. They wield greatswords forged from the heart of dying stars and wield Religion blessings with unparalleled potency. To the righteous, they are beacons of absolute salvation; to the wicked, daemonic, or undead, they are the ultimate arbiters of destruction. To stand before a Seraphim is to be weighed instantly against the cosmic scales of justice.",
