      "Silver Dragon: The Winter Sage",
      "Enormous",
      "Dragon (Elemental/Arcane)",
      "",
      "A breathtaking sight with scales like polished plate mail and a crest resembling a regal, spiked crown. Their slender bodies are built for soaring through high-altitude winds rather than raw brawling. A permanent chill of winter air and ozone surrounds them. Silver Dragons have a genuine fascination with mortal history, living among humans as sages, kings, or bards, hoarding artifacts for the stories attached to them. When they take to the sky, it is to protect the balance of the world. They prefer to end a fight without bloodshed, utilizing surgical strikes and freezing mist to de-escalate conflicts, backed by an absolute mastery of wizardry.",
