      "Small",
      "Humanoid (Reptilian)",
      "",
      "Standing barely four feet tall, the Skink is a lithe, crested reptilian darting through the jungle canopy and murky waters. What they lack in the robust strength of their larger kin, they make up for with cunning and sheer speed. They are the eyes and ears of the Lizardman warband, utilizing guerrilla tactics, poisoned weapons, and the treacherous swamp terrain to whittle down enemies before the heavy hitters arrive. A Skink rarely fights fair; they strike from the high branches with blowguns or hurl barbed javelins from the deep reeds, using the toxic flora of their home to lethal effect.",
