    "values": [
      "Sphinx: The Chronos-Guardian",
      "Giant",
      "(Celestial / Boss)",
      "",
      "The Sphinx is a majestic and terrifying fusion: the massive, powerful body of a desert lion, the expansive wings of a great eagle, and the stoic, noble face of a human sovereign. Their eyes don't just see your physical form; they see the threads of your past and the possibilities of your future. A Sphinx doesn't merely ask a question; it imposes a psychic lock on your reality, unwriting the actions of the weak-willed and forcing them to relive failing moments until they are erased from the timeline. To draw your blade against a Sphinx is to fight time itself.",
      "3",
      "6",
      "5",
      "18",
      "12",
      "9",
      "40/80F",
      "4",
