      "Storm Giant: The Tempest-Lord",
      "Titanic",
      "Giant / Elemental Boss",
      "",
      "Standing an impossible 50 feet tall, the Storm Giant is the living embodiment of a world-ending tempest. Their skin resembles the bruised, churning purple-black of a supercell, and their eyes burn like exploding stars. Clad in armor forged from the hearts of dying thunderheads and wielding a greatsword that arcs with the power to split continents, they do not merely command storms—they are the storm. They are philosophers of the sky, spending decades predicting the future through the stars. But if their mountain is threatened, they descend with the fury of a hurricane, using the atmosphere itself as a blade. To stand in their shadow is to stand at the edge of the apocalypse.",
