    "values": [
      "Succubus Matriarch: The Lust-Queen",
      "Large",
      "Fiend (Demon)",
      "",
      "The Matriarch stands nearly 8 feet tall, possessing an otherworldly, shifting beauty that adapts to the deepest desires of whoever looks upon her. Her skin is a soft, bruised violet, and her wings are covered in a fine, velvet-like down that absorbs light. She wears jewelry made of \"Frozen Tears\"—gems formed from the sorrow of those she has betrayed. She views physical combat as a desperate, last-resort failure. In battle, she is a blurring phantom of motion and psychic pressure, turning your own subconscious and allies against you until you are entirely isolated and broken.",
