    "values": [
      "Treant: The Grove-Warden",
      "Giant",
      "Plant (Elemental)",
      "",
      "Standing roughly 20 feet tall, the Grove-Warden is the steadfast defender of the forest borders. While they lack the apocalyptic, slow-burning rage of the Elder-Barks, these animated oaks and pines are brutal, unyielding sentinels. Their bark is thick and grooved, serving as a natural armor that splinters swords and blunts axes. They are not prone to sudden mobilization; rather, they stand perfectly still for decades, blending seamlessly into the treeline until an intruder strikes the first blow. Once provoked, they unleash heavy, crushing sweeps with their massive boughs to pulp the threat into fertilizer.",
