      "The Living Ram\nA towering, prehistoric juggernaut bred specifically to shatter fortified gates and break the morale of entrenched armies. It features a massive, front-heavy bone crest and three forward-facing horns of unbreakable bone. Because of its Giant size, its physical damage and wound pool are exponentially multiplied, making it a walking catastrophe on the battlefield. It is completely devoid of tactical nuance; it is pointed at a target by its beastmasters, enraged, and set loose. When the Siege Beast charges, the earth violently trembles, and the only viable",
