      "Tri-woven Robes, Staff of the Third Eye",
      "Tri-Strike Staff (+1)",
      "None",
      "Passive Traits\nTriple Mind: The Weaver is immune to Mind-Altering, Charming, and Illusion effects. It rolls all Awareness/Perception checks with Advantage because three minds are always watching.\n\nHarmonic Warding: Any incoming spell damage is automatically reduced by 3. If a spell deals an exact multiple of 3 in damage, the spell is entirely absorbed and converted into +1 Focus.\n\nHovering Step: The Weaver floats 3 feet off the ground, ignoring difficult terrain, ground-based traps, and leaving no tracks or sound.\n\nActions\nTriumvirate Blas(TN6) - Casting Cost: 2: Fires 3 arcane bolts at up to 3 different targets. Make 3 separate casting attacks. Each successful hit deals 1d10 + 24 Casting bonus damage.\n\nTriangle of Binding(TN8) - Casting Cost: 2: Connects 3 enemies in a glowing ethereal triangle. Targets must make a Willpower(6) Save. On a failure, they are Paralyzed for 1 round and share any damage dealt to the other bound targets.\n\nTrifold Restoration(TN7) - Casting Cost: 2): Heals up to 3 allies. Each ally restores 1d10 + Casting heal bonus Wounds and is cleansed of 1 negative condition."
