      "Troll: The Mire-Brute",
      "Large",
      "Monstrosity (Giant-Kin)",
      "",
      "The Mire-Brute is a hulking, foul-smelling abomination that makes its home in stagnant swamps, abandoned sewers, or under rotting bridges. Standing over 10 feet tall, its body is disproportionate, with massive, elongated arms that drag along the ground and a hunched back covered in pustules. Its rubbery, grey-green flesh seethes with hyper-cellular regeneration; you can literally watch its wounds knit back together and severed limbs twitch as they try to reattach. It reeks of copper, rotting meat, and stomach acid, driven by a metabolism that requires it to constantly consume living flesh just to fuel its violently regenerating cells.",
