      "True Dragon: The Calamity of Ages",
      "Enormous",
      "Dragon / Deity",
      "",
      "Unlike the animalistic Wyvern, a True Dragon is an elemental deity in physical form. They are ancient, arrogant, and possess a hoard of knowledge and gold that can destabilize entire kingdoms. They do not merely live in the world; they shape its geography and its history. To fight a True Dragon is to fight a fundamental force of nature with the intellect of a thousand scholars.",
