    "values": [
      "Unicorn: The Pure-Point",
      "Large",
      "Celestial (Beast)",
      "",
      "A Unicorn appears as a horse of impossible perfection, radiating a soft, silver-white luminescence. Its coat feels like spun silk, and its hooves do not touch the ground, pressing against the air millimeters above it and leaving glowing floral patterns in their wake. Its most striking feature is the Spiral Horn (the Alicorn), a weapon made of solidified moonlight that can pierce through illusions and physical armor with equal ease. While gentle with the innocent, a Unicorn becomes a terrifying avatar of wrath when facing Undead, Daemons, or those with blackened hearts. It does not speak, projecting a calm, psychic presence that acts as a natural truth-detector.",
