      "The Alicorn",
      "None",
      "Passive Traits\nThe Pure-Point (Armor & Illusion Piercing): The Unicorn's Alicorn is made of solidified moonlight that cuts through falsehoods. The Unicorn's Melee attacks completely ignore all Armor Mitigation provided by physical armor, shields, or magical barriers (using only the target's natural bodily mitigation). Furthermore, its mere presence shatters falsehoods; any active illusion, invisibility, or magical disguise within 60 feet of the Unicorn is instantly and permanently dispelled.\n\nAir-Treading Hooves: Because its hooves float millimeters above the ground, the Unicorn ignores all difficult terrain, leaves no physical tracks (only temporary glowing floral patterns), and cannot trigger pressure plates, ground traps, or tremorsense. It can even walk seamlessly across the surface of deep water or thin air for short gaps.\n\nWrath of the Innocent (Light-Soul): The Unicorn is the ultimate bane of corruption. Whenever it attacks a target classified as Undead, Daemon, or any creature currently inflicted with a Curse or Disease, the Unicorn gains automatic Advantage on its To-Hit and To-Cast rolls, and all resulting Wounds are doubled.\n\nAction-Based Abilities\nAvatar of Wrath(TN9) (Casting Cost: 2 Actions): The Unicorn rears back, its horn erupting in a blinding flash of silver-white star-fire. All enemies within a 20-foot radius must pass an Agility(10) test or take 25 Radiant Wounds and gain the Blinded condition for 1 round.\n\nMoonlight Charge (Melee Cost: 2 Actions): The Unicorn lowers its Alicorn and charges in a straight line up to its maximum Movement (40). Make a Melee attack (+4 To-Hit) against the first target in its path. If successful, it deals 2d10 + 25 Wounds. If the target is a corrupted creature (Undead/Daemon) or has a \"blackened heart\" (decided by the GM), the sheer radiant trauma forces them to pass a severe Willpower(16) test or suffer 2 Stunned conditions.\n\nPsychic Truth-Detector (Cost: 1 Action): The Unicorn pulses a wave of calming, revealing psychic energy in a 40-foot radius. Any enemy caught in the radius must pass a Willpower(10) test or lose their hostility, dropping their weapons and instantly losing 1 Action on their next turn. Simultaneously, this pure light washes over all allies in the radius, instantly curing them of any Fear, Charm, or Poison conditions.\n\nSilver-Light Banishment(TN10) (Casting Cost: 2 Actions): The Unicorn rears back, and its Alicorn flares with blinding, concentrated starlight in a 30-foot cone. Make a Casting roll (+8 To-Cast) against all enemies in the cone. On a success, they take 3d10 + 35 Radiant Wounds and are permanently Blinded until magically cured. Undead and Daemons caught in this blast must pass a severe Willpower test or be instantly banished back to the grave or their home plane."
    ],
