    "values": [
      "Vampire: The Crimson Lord",
      "Medium",
      "Undead (Apex Predator)",
      "",
      "The Crimson Lord is not a mindless, rotting corpse, but a terrifying apex predator wrapped in the guise of aristocratic perfection. Pale, impossibly graceful, and possessing a gaze that can paralyze a charging knight, the Vampire views mortals as nothing more than cattle and fine wine. They move in blurs of unnatural speed, capable of shifting their physical form into mist to evade blows. In combat, they do not just seek to kill; they seek to subjugate, charm, and drain their victims dry, using the party's own blood to knit their undead flesh back together. To fight a Crimson Lord is to realize you have willingly walked into a slaughterhouse dressed as a ballroom.",
