    "values": [
      "Vulkan-Kahn (The First Forge)",
      "Enormous",
      "Elemental (Pantheon Boss)",
      "",
      ": A god-like entity of the Pyreborn pantheon. Vulkan-Kahn stands nearly 30 feet tall when bipedal. He is a terrifying fusion of feline elegance and volcanic raw power. His fur is not hair, but a dense mesh of white-hot needles that shimmer like burning silk. His black stripes are actually deep fissures in his hide, pulsing with the rhythmic glow of a tectonic heart. To the Pyreborn, he is the \"First Forge,\" the being from whom all heat originated. He bridges the gap between the Enormous and Titanic scale, combining the terrifying agility of an apex feline predator with the apocalyptic damage multipliers of a world-ending boss.",
