    "values": [
      "Warrior Chaos (Iron-Bound)",
      "Medium",
      "Humanoid (Corrupted)",
      "",
      "The faceless foot soldiers of the dark gods. Where the Champion is a singular engine of destruction that shatters the line, the Iron-Bound are the unyielding anvil that holds it. Encased in crude, heavy iron armor and driven by endless bloodlust, they have traded their humanity for unnatural strength and resilience. They march in lockstep, an unthinking, unfeeling tide of spikes, thick shields, and rusted axes. They do not strategize, and they do not retreat; they simply advance, hacking away at the enemy until the battlefield is drowned in blood.",
