    "values": [
      "Warrior of Chaos (Champion)",
      "Medium",
      "Humanoid (Corrupted)",
      "",
      "A towering monolith of dark iron, spiked plate, and unholy devotion. The Champion Warrior of Chaos has surrendered their humanity to the dark gods, gaining unnatural strength and resilience in return. They do not feel pain, they do not tire, and they march across the battlefield like a walking slaughterhouse. Where the human soldier holds the line, the Chaos Warrior shatters it. Beneath the horned helm, there is no longer a man—only an empty, bloodthirsty vessel driven by the whispering will of ruin.",
