    "values": [
      "Werewolf: The Sun-Sentry",
      "Large",
      "Lycanthrope (Blood-Bound)",
      "",
      "Unlike wild lycanthropes that shift with the lunar cycle, the Sun-Sentry is a werewolf bound by vampiric blood-magic. Permanently locked in a towering, 9-foot bipedal hybrid form, their sole purpose is to serve as the daytime protectors for slumbering vampires. They possess thick, matted fur that deflects blades, and musculature dense enough to crush a knight's helmet with a single bite. They do not fear the sun; they embrace it, standing guard over crypts and shadowed manors, relying on their supernatural senses to tear apart vampire hunters long before they can reach the master's coffin.",
