    "values": [
      "White Dragon: The Blizzard Stalker",
      "Giant",
      "Dragon / Beast",
      "",
      "Unlike its scheming, manipulative cousins, the White Dragon is a creature of pure, feral instinct. It is a savage apex predator of the frozen wastes, driven by hunger and territorial rage rather than a desire for gold or dominion. Its scales are the color of packed snow and glacial ice, allowing it to vanish completely into a whiteout. It hunts like a massive, winged leopard, clinging to sheer ice walls or burrowing under deep snow to ambush prey, tearing them apart before they even realize the blizzard has teeth.\n\nMove: 50 Ground / 40 Burrow (Ice) / 80 Flight",
