      "1",
      "Blackened Rune Plate, Warden's Glaive (or Soul-Mace)",
      "Warden's Glaive",
      "Special Abilities",
      "Passive Traits\nCrypt-Commander (Aura): The Warden is the catalyst of the undead line. All allied Undead within 30 feet of the Knight gain a +1 bonus to their Melee To-Hit and completely ignore the Turn Undead or Frightened conditions as long as the Knight remains standing.\n\nLife-Siphon Blade: Every time the Wight deals damage to a living target’s Wounds, it regains 5 Wounds as it drinks the escaping life force.\n\nMartial Memory: The Wight studies and remembers mortal techniques in real-time. If an enemy attacks the Grave Knight with the exact same Melee or Ranged weapon twice in a row, the attacker automatically suffers Disadvantage on the second strike (and all subsequent strikes with that weapon) as the Knight perfectly predicts and parries the blow.\n\nRune-Etched Bones: The creature is completely immune to Necrotic damage. Furthermore, because it is a skeletal entity beneath the armor, it takes half damage from all Piercing weapons (arrows and spears simply pass through the empty ribs).\n\nAction-Based Abilities\nBlackened Strike (Melee Cost: 2 Actions): Type: Melee Attack. Effect: Deals 2d10 + 28 wounds. If this attack hits, the target must pass a Willpower(10) check or suffer -3 to their next Attack Roll as the cold of the grave numbs their limbs.\n\nExecutioner's Parry (Melee Cost: 1 Action / Reaction): The Knight can hold 1 Action to use as a Reaction. When struck by a Melee attack, it rolls a Physical test against the attacker's To-Hit. On a success, the Knight takes zero damage, effortlessly parrying the blow, and immediately deals 10 unmitigable Slashing Wounds in a riposte.\n\nSilent Directive (Cost: 1 Action): The Knight strikes the butt of its glaive against the earth. Up to three allied Undead within 40 feet may immediately use a Reaction to move up to half their speed without triggering counter-attacks, allowing the Knight to flawlessly reposition the battle line.\n\nWarden's Cleave (Cost: 2 Actions): A textbook, disciplined strike with the heavy glaive. Make a Melee attack (+5 To-Hit) with a 10-foot reach. If successful, it deals 1d10 + 28 Slashing/Necrotic Wounds."
    ],
