    "values": [
      "Woodland Spirit",
      "Medium",
      "Elemental (Plant)",
      "",
      "A Spiny Bark Sprite looks more like a sentient bundle of kindling than a living creature. Their bodies are composed of knotted, iron-hard heartwood, with sharp, thorn-like protrusions acting as both armor and weaponry. Faded brown leaves and patches of grey lichen cling to their limbs, providing perfect camouflage against the autumn floor or the trunks of dying trees. They are fiercely territorial and possess a hive-like intelligence. When one Sprite is threatened, the entire grove awakens. They don't speak in words, but in the sound of rubbing branches and the snap of dry twigs. To a traveler, they are nearly invisible until the moment the \"vines\" start to pull at their ankles.",
