    "values": [
      "Xaver: The Glass-Spined Stalker",
      "Medium",
      "Monstrosity (Hybrid / Skirmisher)",
      "",
      "The Xaver is a hexapedal mammalian-reptilian hybrid. It has the lean, powerful body of a cheetah, but is covered in flexible, diamond-hard scales that act like fiber optics, seamlessly bending light around its body. Its most striking feature is the row of crystalline spines running down its back, capable of vibrating at frequencies that shatter glass and eardrums alike. It doesn't hunt with scent or sight in the traditional sense; it \"sees\" through Photonic Resonance, detecting the minute light distortions caused by the movement of living souls. When a Xaver is about to strike, its spines glow with a prismatic light, and the air around it begins to hum with high-frequency energy.",
