    "values": [
      "Xochitonal: The Guardian of the Sun-Blood",
      "Enormous",
      "Mythical / Reptilian",
      "",
      "A titan-class reptile, easily 40 feet long, with scales possessing the texture and diamond-hardness of obsidian. Its skin is etched with glowing, turquoise Aztec-style glyphs that pulse with the rhythm of a dying sun. Xochitonal does not just guard a physical place, but a cosmic barrier; to pass it is to cross from life into the eternal dark. As a leader, it possesses a hive-mind connection to all cold-blooded creatures in its vicinity. It commands the very water around it, turning rivers into crushing fists, and its dreaded \"Soul-Anchor\" bite tethers a victim's spirit to the earth, ensuring they can neither flee the battle nor be resurrected if they fall.",
