      "Yeti: The Blizzard-Stalker",
      "Large",
      "Monstrosity / Beast",
      "",
      "Standing 9 to 11 feet tall, the Yeti is a mountain of corded muscle covered in thick, matted white fur. It doesn't just survive the deadly cold of the high peaks; it weaponizes it. To a Yeti, a blinding blizzard is the perfect hunting ground. They are incredibly territorial and possess a primal, cruel cunning—often burying themselves in snowdrifts to ambush travelers, or using their deafening roars to trigger localized avalanches that crush entire caravans beneath tons of ice.",
