      "Yuan-ti Abomination: The Serpent-Blooded",
      "Large",
      "Monstrosity / Serpent",
      "",
      "Sitting at the terrifying apex of their rigid caste system, Abominations are massive hybrids possessing humanoid torsos and the lower bodies of colossal serpents. Biologically incapable of feeling traditional human emotions like love, fear, or remorse, they operate on a cold, intellectual scale of \"benefit versus cost.\" They prefer the \"whisper over the fang,\" using poison, suggestion magic, and political subversion to topple kingdoms from the inside. When they are finally forced onto the battlefield, they strike with surgical precision, executing their enemies with unblinking, sociopathic efficiency.",
