      "Zephyr: Greater Hurricane-Core",
      "Giant",
      "Elemental (Air)",
      "",
      "If a standard Zephyr is a deadly cyclone, the Greater Zephyr is a living hurricane. Towering over sixty feet tall, this sentient vortex of violently pressurized air, screaming wind, and pulverized debris is a walking natural disaster. Born only in the most catastrophic magical storms or summoned by the highest echelon of sky-cults, it obliterates anything in its path with terrifying indifference. It doesn't wield weapons; it wields the environment itself, sucking up boulders, wagons, and armored knights into its funnel before violently ejecting them. To stand before a Greater Zephyr is to challenge the wrath of the sky itself.",
