      "Zephyr: The Dust-Devil",
      "Medium",
      "Elemental (Air)",
      "",
      "A lesser manifestation of sentient wind, the Dust-Devil is a chaotic, knee-to-shoulder-high funnel of rapidly spinning air, sand, and loose gravel. Lacking the cohesive power to slice through plate armor, they instead act as elemental scavengers or the frontline fodder for sky-cults. They are mindless and erratic, completely devoid of self-preservation. When a flock of Dust-Devils descends, they don't seek to crush their enemies; they seek to overwhelm them, filling the air with blinding grit and suffocating dust while whipping exposed skin with thousands of tiny, razor-sharp stones.",
