      "Zombie: The Shambling Plague",
      "Medium",
      "Undead",
      "",
      "The Shambling Plague is a relentless, bloated corpse driven entirely by the hunger for living flesh and the dark magic that forces it to walk. Unlike skeletons, zombies are wet, heavy, and highly infectious. They feel no pain, possess no self-preservation, and are barely slowed down by missing limbs. A single zombie is a nuisance; a horde of them is a slow-moving, suffocating avalanche of rotting meat that drags its victims down under sheer, suffocating weight to feast.",
